citations.desc: ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 10:15-10:45
am on 06-DEC-16.
Phone numbers were called, vehicle horn was honked several times; gate was locked so could not knock on door.
Accompanied by MDA inspectors
